<font face="comic sans ms" size="3"><p>&nbsp;</p><p><font color="#000099">We aim to ensure each child is fully prepared for their reception year at school working towards the Early Learning Goals required by the Nursery Education Grant Scheme and to comply with The Code of Practice.</font><br></p></font>
